profile:
Imagine your home totally organized! At Closets by Design, we work to simplify your life by designing, building, and installing custom closets, garage cabinets, home offices, laundries, pantries, and much more. With a wide selection of finishes, accessories, and hardware, you will get the customized look you have always dreamed of and you can rely on our three decades of experience for total customer satisfaction. From our no obligation in-home consultation, custom tailored designs, and high quality product construction, we offer excellent value. For service in Toronto and Durham including Toronto Downtown, North York, Scarborough, Pickering, Ajax, Whitby, Oshawa, Uxbridge, Newcastle, Peterborough, and Bowmanville visit our website to book your free consultation today or visit our showroom in Toronto located at 667 Mount Pleasant Rd. or Scarborough 780 Birchmount Rd, Unit 8.    
Closets by Design: Quality, beauty, and commitment are built in!

profile:
Tailored Living Markham and Durham Region has the strength of 20+ years of franchising experience behind it as one of the family of brands of Home Franchise Concepts (HFC). Each of our independently owned and operated franchise locations provides the very best in high-quality storage and home organization systems for homes and businesses. Through free, in-home or on-site consultations, expert measurement, innovative design and professional installation, your home or business transformation is custom-tailored to your needs and specifications.

As your local custom closet and organizational Specialists, Tailored Living Markham and Durham Region is dedicated to bringing Markham and the surrounding areas outstanding service and personalized organization solutions to fit your home and lifestyle. Let us help you find the best storage solutions for your home and garage. Call now for your in-home consultation. We look forward to meeting you! Custom closets, built-ins, Murphy Beds, Storage and Garage Floor Solutions. Design and installation. Let us make your vision a reality!

Check us out on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TailoredlivingMarkham/

profile:
Gum Tree Cabinets offers beautiful and functional solutions for your living space.  We specialize in completely custom products from closet organizers, smart office solutions, fireplace and entertainment units with stunning built-in shelving to space-saving wall beds.  Organizing your home has never been easier with our innovative products and accessories!

Gum Tree Cabinets is a one stop, full service, quality supplier. We never outsource our installations and you will always interact with the owners of the company. We look forward to working with your family to ensure your complete satisfaction.
